prints.title: Doraemon Lamp
prints.description: A cute Doraemon character nightlight, printed in segments and assembled with LED internals.
prints.notes: Multi-color print using AMS. The LED diffusion through the white PLA works beautifully.

prints.title: Labubu Figure
prints.description: A detailed Labubu character figure with intricate surface details.
prints.notes: Painted after printing for the gradient effect. Fine layer height for surface detail.

prints.title: Platform 9 3/4 Sign
prints.description: A replica of the famous Harry Potter platform sign, perfect for any wizard's room.
prints.notes: Multi-color swap print. The gold filament really makes it pop!

prints.title: Remote Control Holder
prints.description: A practical organizer for TV remotes and small electronics.
prints.notes: PETG for durability. Designed with rounded edges for comfort.

prints.title: Xbox Controller Stand
prints.description: A sleek stand for displaying and charging Xbox controllers.
prints.notes: Clean design that matches the Xbox aesthetic.

prints.title: KFC Bag Model
prints.description: A quirky replica of the iconic KFC bucket bag, scaled down.
prints.notes: Fun conversation piece. Multi-color print with hand-painted details.

prints.title: Kansas City Chiefs Logo
prints.description: A 3D printed Kansas City Chiefs arrowhead logo for displaying team spirit.
prints.notes: Go Chiefs! Perfect for game day display.

prints.title: Custom M Case
prints.description: A custom protective case with the letter M design.
prints.notes: TPU for flexibility and shock absorption. Custom fit.

prints.title: Victory Hand Sign
prints.description: A peace sign / victory hand gesture sculpture.
prints.notes: Detailed finger articulation required careful support placement.

prints.title: Articulated Hand Model
prints.description: A fully articulated anatomical hand model with movable joints.
prints.notes: Print-in-place articulation. Great for anatomy study or display.

prints.title: Modular Storage Box
prints.description: A stackable storage box for small items and components.
prints.notes: PETG for the clear finish. Perfect for organizing small parts.
